 e.g  channel '0.1 MeV' contains the spectrum between 0.1 and 0.2 MeV.
(The dmp folder provides spectra with 1 keV resolution.
 There is also a spectrum of pre-saddle gammas.)
 
The energy spectrum shows the energies of the nuclear gamma transitions.
Measured gamma spectra are smeared out by the doppler shift due to the
emission from the moving fragments.
 
